summary: So, for the record, YES, I am writing that superhero AU thing. It will be a one-shot (for now), just kinda something for fun,...
body: So, for the record, YES, I am writing that superhero AU thing. It will be a one-shot (for now), just kinda something for fun, intended to sorta pay homage to a lot of the magical girl anime, and the Henshin Tokusatsu shows throughout the years. But tht thing about that is I have a number of really fun ideas for it….but by that token, that means I have to write quite a bit, so it may take a little bit to get finished. But I figured I might as well show the opening bit, as a preview. You guys deserve that, at least. Oh, and Magical Girl Retsuko has a proper name: Pretty-Rage.
